Iustic̃. uicecõib. Prepositis. Ministris. & om̃ib prob̃ ho-
minib tociꝰ t̾re sue. cl̾icis & laicis saltm̃ Sciant p̾sentes &
fut᷑i nos ad honorẽ d̃i & gl̾iose uͥgĩs marie & sanctissimi Re-
gis Edwardi .&. ad exaltacõem sc̃e religionis ꝓ salute nr̃a &
oĩm añcessoꝵ & successoꝵ nr̃oꝵ & ꝓ aĩab illustris regis Will̃i
pat̾s nr̃i. & Ermẽgardis Regine mr̃is nr̃e & oĩm añcessoꝵ &
successoꝵ nr̃oꝵ qͣndã abb̃iam cist̾ciensis ordĩs fundasse apͩ bal-
m᷑ynach in fyff̃. nosq monachis ip̃ius ordĩs ibid̃ d̃o seruiẽtib &
in ꝑpetuũ seruitur̾ dedisse & cõcessisse ⁊ hac carta nr̃a ꝯfͥmasse
totã t̾rã de cultͣn. & balm᷑ynach in fyff̃ cũ oĩb ꝑtinẽciis suis. .s. bal
lindan. & ballindard. & corbi ꝑ suas rͨtas diuisas & cũ oĩb aliis ad
p̾dcãs t̾ras iuste ꝑtinẽtib Quas eciã adam de stawel fr̃ ⁊ heres Ri
cardi Reuel nob̾ ad opꝰ dñe Ermẽgardis regine mr̃is nr̃e in plena cu-
ria nr̃a apͩ forfar qͥetas clamauͭ. & in manu nr̃a ꝓ se & h̾edib suis ꝑ
fustũ & baculũ resignauit Cõcessimꝰ eciã p̾fatis monachis cist̾ciensis
ordinis ad fundacõem p̾nõiate abb̃ie fethmure in anegus ꝑ suas rͨtas
diuisas & oĩb iustis ꝑtinẽciis suis. Et nos ⁊ h̾edes nr̃i manutenebi
mus & warãtizabimꝰ p̾dc̃is monachis p̾dc̃as t̾ras cũ om̃ib ꝑtinẽciis
& lib̾tatib suis inꝑpetuũ cõtra om̃s hoĩes Qͣre uolumꝰ ut predc̃i mo
nachi om̃s p̾dc̃as terras habeant & teneãt de nob̾ & successorib nr̃is
in lib̾am. purã. qͥetã & ꝑpetuam elemosinã In t̾ris & aquis. in pͣtis
& pascuis. in moris & marisiis. in stangnis & molendinis in uiis &
seĩtis. In salinis & piscariis. & oĩb aliis aisiamẽtis ad p̾dc̃as t̾ras iuste
ꝑtinẽtib. Ita lib̾e & qͥete. plenarie ⁊ honorifice sicut aliqͣ elemosina
lib̾ius & qͥetiꝰ. pleniꝰ & honorificẽciꝰ ab auxiliis. ex̾citib talliagiis tol
leneis & oĩb exaccõnib. cõsuetudinib & seruiciis secl̃arib in regno
Scocie tenet᷑ aut possidet᷑. Ita ꝙ nichil hoꝵ oĩno p̾ter solas or̃ones ab
eis ꝑ totũ regnũ Scocie possit exigi Test̃ Andrea ep̃o morauie. Wal
tero cumĩ cõite de meninteh. Walt̾o olyfard iustic̃ Laodonie. Wal-
tero filio Alani senescallo & iust̃ scoc̃. Comite Patricio. henrico
de Ball̃. thom̃ de Hay Ioh̃e & Walt̾o fr̃ib suis. thom̃ fil̃ Ran-
dulfi. Galfrido & Will̃o de Nithyn cl̾icis nr̃is apͩ Clacmanan.
t̾cia die februarii. anno regni nr̃i septimo decimo
De Balm᷑ynach
